
Direct/Tango/Swap positions with any Piece within movement range.

Passive/Rain Dance/Leave behind a Storm Tile when moving from a tile. If an Enemy on a Storm Tile takes 2 or more damage, Lightning strikes them for an additional 2 damage.

Indirect/Shuriken Storm/Throw a Shuriken in each of the 6 hex diagonal directions, dealing 2 damage to the first enemies hit. Projectiles are blocked by other Heroes.